<tr>
		 <td>
              <p><strong><a name="2" id="2">Do I need a separate router or wireless access point?</a></strong></p>
              
              <p>No. Unlike other solutions on the market, you do not need a separate router or wireless access point. Your Portus Home gateway is a fully integrated wireless broadband gateway, which connects directly to your existing DSL or cable modem. The Portus Home gateway integrates a Wi-Fi access point, router, firewall, and 4 port switch.  You can use your Portus Home gateway for all your home networking requirements. 	</p>
              
                       <div class="dividerDashLine"/></div>
 		 </td>
</tr>
<tr>
		 <td>
             <p><strong><a name="3" id="3">Will I need to install special software?</a></strong></p>
              
              <p>No special software is required. The user interface of your Portus Home system is completely browser based. No matter where you are, you can access and control your Portus Home system completely through an Internet browser or compatible web-enabled mobile phone.</p>
              
             
              <div class="dividerDashLine"/></div>
		 </td>
</tr>
<tr>
		 <td>
              <p><strong><a name="4" id="4">Do I need to pre-wire my house to use Portus Home?</a></strong></p>
              
              <p>Portus Home is 100% wireless so no pre-wiring of your home is required.</p>
              <div class="dividerDashLine"/></div>
		 </td>
</tr>
<tr>
		 <td>
              <p><strong><a name="5" id="5">Is a subscription to the Portus Home service required?</a></strong></p>
              
              <p>In order to use your Portus Home system, you need to subscribe to the Portus Home service. This can be on a month by month basis or you can purchase an annual subscription at a discount. </p>
         <div class="dividerDashLine"/></div>
