             <p><strong><a name="6" id="6">Do I need a computer to run my Portus Home system?</a></strong></p>
             
             <p>
The Portus Home solution is completely self contained and doesn’t need a computer to operate. All you need is your Portus Home gateway, a broadband Internet connection, and your choice of devices to begin using your Portus Home system. To access your Portus Home system, you can use any device that has a web browser, including touch panels, computers, PDAs and compatible web-enabled mobile phones.  </p>
<div class="dividerDashLine"/></div>
