             <p><strong><a name="8" id="8">How do I connect my Portus Home cameras?</a></strong></p>
             
             <p>Portus Home cameras are wireless IP cameras and connect directly to the Portus Home gateway via Wi-Fi. You don’t need a separate wireless access point or router to connect your Portus Home cameras. </p>
             
                      <div class="dividerDashLine"/></div>
		 </td>
</tr>
