		 <td>
             <p><strong><a name="9" id="9">How secure is my Portus Home system?</a></strong></p>
             
             <p>Portus Home integrates layers upon layers of security to protect your system and your privacy. Not only does the Portus Home gateway integrate robust firewall technology, but all communications occur over encrypted links. Only fully authenticated users can access the Portus Home system remotely. Portus remote access servers are located in secure hosting facilities and subject to third-party security audits to ensure your information remains safe at all times.

</p>
         <div class="dividerDashLine"/></div>
