            <p><strong><a name="10" id="10">Does Portus Home work with my existing security system? </a></strong></p>

            
            <p>Your Portus Home system includes a self monitored home security application that works separately from your existing security system, providing a real-time view of what's happening with your home and family, from wherever you are, giving you the ability to monitor any situation and take whatever action is required.	</p>
